Hi!

So apparently the last map I uploaded wasn't my last upload.
I got a request to upload this map here and I am glad of that!

So, here it is.
My second mg map for CS:S after the original mg_ZeiZeiii. I have to warn you, it is sometimes VERY buggy, but there is nothing I can do to it now. But it is totally playable and many of my server players really enjoyed it.

As I hinted, it is 5years old map, so expect some craziness!
